NK016(ma)019:0: drag dmar 'o bran lugs kyi sgrub thabs dngos grub char 'bebs bzhugs /
NK016(ma)019:1: drag dmar 'o bran lugs kyi sgrub thabs dngos grub char 'bebs bzhugs /
NK016(ma)019:3: chos nyid zhi las g.yo med kyang //
NK016(ma)019:4: gdug gtum dregs pa'i gnyen po ru //
NK016(ma)019:5: cher khros dbang brag lhag pa'i lhar //
NK016(ma)019:6: btud nas sgrub thabs mdo tsam bshad //
NK016(ma)019:7: 'dir drag dmar 'o bran lugs su grags pa'i sgrub thabs la gsum /
NK016(ma)019:9: sbyor ba'i chos la drug gi /
NK016(ma)019:11: rgyun gyi rnal 'byor dang tshogs mchod rtsam la /
NK016(ma)019:13: nyer spyod sogs nyer mkho'i yo byad thams cad tshogs par bsham mo //
NK016(ma)019:14: gnyis pa tshogs bsags pa ni /
NK016(ma)019:15: ho sku gsum lha tshogs nam mkha' khyab pa la
NK016(ma)019:16: phyag 'tshal gus mchod sdig bshags yi rang 'bul ka
NK016(ma)019:17: dag chos dbyings klong du skyabs su mchi 'gro kun
NK016(ma)019:18: sgrol phyir rdo rje'i sems bskyed do zhes lan gsum
NK016(ma)019:20: rdo rje slob dpon sangs rgyas dpal sogs kyang bya'o //
NK016(ma)019:22: bgegs bskrad pa ni h'u nyon cig bgegs dang log
NK016(ma)019:23: 'dren tshogs gsang spyod lta bar mi dbang zhing byang
NK016(ma)019:24: chub sgrub la bar chod rnams mchod spyin bzang pos
NK016(ma)019:25: tshim byos la myur ba nyid du phyir dengs shig
NK016(ma)019:26: gal te bka' las 'da' byed na sprul pa'i khro
NK016(ma)019:27: tshogs mang po yis rdul du rlog par gdon mi
NK016(ma)019:28: za drags sngags brjod la bskrad /
NK016(ma)019:29: bzhi ba mtshams bcad ba ni /
NK016(ma)019:30: h'u nga ni ye nas rang byung ba'i sangs rgyas
NK016(ma)019:31: kun gyi 'khor los bsgyur che mchog drag po thod
NK016(ma)019:32: phreng rtsal thugs las khro chung mtshon cha dang rab
NK016(ma)019:33: 'bar me yi tsh+wa tsh+wa 'phro phyogs mtshams kun tu
NK016(ma)019:34: rab tu gtams bar chad kun gyis mi phyed pa'i
NK016(ma)019:35: gzhom med rdo rje'i gur du gyur badz+ra kro d+ha
NK016(ma)019:36: tsakra dz+wa la ram h'u b+h+rum lnga pa byin dbab
NK016(ma)019:37: pa ni h'u chos sku zhi ba'i ngang las ma
NK016(ma)019:38: g.yos kyang gzugs sku 'jig byed khro bo'i skur ston
NK016(ma)019:39: pa dbang drag rol pa'i dkyil 'khor lha tshogs rnams
NK016(ma)019:40: glog ltar myur ba'i thugs rjes brtser dgongs la 'dir
NK016(ma)019:41: gshegs dbang bskur byin phob dngos grub stsol ngo mtshar
NK016(ma)019:42: rtags dang mtshan ma myur du stonah badz+ra gu ru
NK016(ma)019:43: kro d+ha r+aa dza sa ma ya a be sha
NK016(ma)019:44: ya a a drug pa mchod rdzas byin rlobs ni
NK016(ma)019:45: ram yam kham rnam dag chos dbying ngang nyid las
NK016(ma)019:46: rang byung mchod pa'i phung po ni kun bzang mchod
NK016(ma)019:47: pa'i sprin lta bu dpag yas nam mkha' gang bar
NK016(ma)019:48: gyur badz+ra ar+g+ham nas shap+da sarba pany+tsa a mri ta
NK016(ma)019:49: rak+ta ba ling ta +aah h'u gnyis pa dngos gzhi
NK016(ma)019:50: la bdun gyis dang po lha bskyed pa ni stong
NK016(ma)019:51: nyid snying rje zung du 'jug pas /
NK016(ma)019:52: h'u rdo rje sa gzhir gur bla re 'khrigs ye
NK016(ma)019:53: shes me ri kha dog rnam lnga 'bar phyi rol
NK016(ma)019:54: gser 'khor me 'khor rtsibs stong 'bar rtsibs stong sprul
NK016(ma)019:55: ba'i pho nya lcags sdig 'gyed dbus su 'byung bzhi
NK016(ma)019:56: ri rab pad+ma'i steng sna tshogs rdo rje'i lte bar
NK016(ma)019:57: gzhal yas khang mtshan nyid yongs rdzogs drag po'i rgyan
NK016(ma)019:58: gyis spras rtsibs brgyad 'khor lo'i lte bar chos 'byung
NK016(ma)019:59: dbus // rdo rje h'u yig 'bar ba'i 'phro 'du
NK016(ma)019:60: las khro rgyal pad+ma drag po he ru ka me
NK016(ma)019:61: dpung ltar dmar khros 'khrugs rngams pa'i gzugs //
NK016(ma)019:62: phyag g.yas rdo rje rtse dgu nam mkhar phyar phyag
NK016(ma)019:63: g.yon thugs sprul lcags sdig nag po ni mig dgu
NK016(ma)019:64: bsgrad cing kha dgus dgra bgegs za bco brgyad r+aa
NK016(ma)019:65: yis gdon bgegs snying nas 'dzin yang sprul nyid sbrul
NK016(ma)019:66: stong gsum 'gengs pa 'dzin thod skam dbu rgyan mgo
NK016(ma)019:67: rlon do shal 'phyang zhal gdangs mche gtsigs spyan gsum
NK016(ma)019:68: dmar zlum bgrad dbu skra sma ra smin ma me
NK016(ma)019:69: bzhin 'bar dpal gyi chas brgyad gar gyi nyams dgur
NK016(ma)019:70: ldan pang na yum chen rdo rje mkha' 'gro sngo
NK016(ma)019:71: gri thod 'dzin pas 'khyud cing gnyis med sbyor thugs
NK016(ma)019:72: kar phyag na rdo rje mthon mthing mdog phyag g.yas
NK016(ma)019:73: rdo rje g.yon pas sdigs mdzub mdzad gser gyi mchod
NK016(ma)019:74: rten bum par sku brten bzhugs gtso bo'i spyi bor
NK016(ma)019:75: pad+ma sam b+ha wa mthing ga rdo rje thod pa
NK016(ma)019:76: kha t+aam bsnams 'dzum zhal mdzes ldan za 'og ber
NK016(ma)019:77: chen gsol she'u'i snyan zhu rgod ldem rtse sgros brgyan
NK016(ma)019:78: spyi bo'i gtsug na sprul pa'i mkha' lding ni spu
NK016(ma)019:79: gri'i me gshog 'bar ba g.yob cing rdab phyogs bzhi'i
NK016(ma)019:80: rtsibs la rigs bzhi'i mkha' 'gro ni dkar ser dmar
NK016(ma)019:81: ljang gri thod kha t+aam 'dzin gar stabs kyis 'gying
NK016(ma)019:82: bde ba'i ro yis gang mtshams bzhir bcud ldan rin
NK016(ma)019:83: chen bum pas brgyan shar sgor gsang bdag phyag rdor
NK016(ma)019:84: sngon po ni rdo rje phyar zhing sdig mdzub drag
NK016(ma)019:85: por sgreng lho sgor 'jam dpal gshin rje sku mdog
NK016(ma)019:86: ser g.yas pa ral gri g.yon pa sdigs mdzub can
NK016(ma)019:87: nub sgor rta mgrin dmar po rta skad 'tsher dbyug
NK016(ma)019:88: to phyar zhing sdigs mdzub me chen 'bar byang sgor
NK016(ma)019:89: yak+sha me 'bar mthing nag brjid tho chen phyar zhing
NK016(ma)019:90: lcags kyu me 'bar gdengs kun kyang rngam brjid dur
NK016(ma)019:91: khrod chas kyis brgyan ye shes bskal pa'i me dpung
NK016(ma)019:92: sku las 'bar lha tshogs kun gyi gnas gsum yig
NK016(ma)019:93: 'bru gsum rdo rje gsum gyi ngo bos mtshan par
NK016(ma)019:95: gnyis pa ni snying ga'i h'u las 'od zer 'phros
NK016(ma)019:96: pas ye shes kyi 'khor lo spyan drangs par bsams
NK016(ma)019:97: la / h'u rnga yab gling dang o rgyan yul
NK016(ma)019:98: zangs mdog dpal gyi ri bo nas pad+ma drag po
NK016(ma)019:99: 'khor bcas rnams spyan 'dren gnas 'dir gshegs su gsol
NK016(ma)019:100: zhes dang tshig bdun gsol 'debs kyang brjod pa'i mthar
NK016(ma)019:101: e h+ya hi badz+ra sa ma ya dzaphem phem hrim
NK016(ma)019:102: hrim hrim zhes pas spyan drangs /
NK016(ma)019:103: dzah'u bam hosa dgug gzhug bcing mnyes byas te dam ye shes dbyer med du bsam mo //
NK016(ma)019:105: ho rgyal ba rigs lnga'i lha tshogs kyis phyi nang
NK016(ma)019:106: gsang ba'i dbang bskur bas yon tan kun rdzogs 'od
NK016(ma)019:107: dpag med 'khor la gtso bos rgyas btab bo //
NK016(ma)019:110: hoh me tog la sogs phyi mchod rdzas 'dod yon
NK016(ma)019:111: lnga po nang gi rdzas gnyis med 'khril sbyor gsang
NK016(ma)019:112: ba'i rdzas // bdud rtsi lnga po dam tshig rdzas
NK016(ma)019:113: sha lnga la sogs gtor ma'i rdzas rtsa brgyad stong
NK016(ma)019:114: sbyar bdud rtsi sman 'dod chags dag pa rak+ta'i mtsho
NK016(ma)019:115: spros bral ka dag dag mnyam ste mchod sprin rab
NK016(ma)019:116: 'byams gcig bsdus pas dkyil 'khor lha tshogs thams cad
NK016(ma)019:117: mchod ar+g+ham nas shap+da'i bar dang ma h+aa pany+tsa a
NK016(ma)019:118: mri ta kh+aa hi ma h+aa rak+ta kh+aa hi ma
NK016(ma)019:119: h+aa ba lim ta kh+aa hi zhes pas mchod lnga
NK016(ma)019:120: ba'i rdzas // pa ni / h'u rgyal ba kun
NK016(ma)019:121: gyi drag po'i sku nus pa thogs med log 'dren
NK016(ma)019:122: ba'i rdzas // pa ni / 'dzoms // thugs rje
NK016(ma)019:123: rmad byung dkyil 'khor gtso pad+ma thod phreng drag por
NK016(ma)019:124: 'dud zhes pa tsam mam spro na bstod pa gzhan
NK016(ma)019:126: chos kyi dbyings las longs spyod rdzogs skur shar bdud
NK016(ma)019:127: 'dul pad+ma 'byung gnas sprul pa'i sku sku gsum bdag
NK016(ma)019:128: nyid dkyil 'khor kun gyi gtso mkha' ltar kun khyab
NK016(ma)019:129: khyed la phyag 'tshal bstod gnyis med yum mchog rdo
NK016(ma)019:130: rje rnal 'byor ma rigs bzhi mkha' 'gro gsang bdag
NK016(ma)019:131: gshin rje dang rta mgrin me dbal la sogs grangs
NK016(ma)019:132: med 'khor chu zla'i rol par ston la phyag 'tshal
NK016(ma)019:134: thugs ka'i sa bon sngags kyis bskor //
NK016(ma)019:135: de las 'od 'phros stong gsum gang bgegs bcom rgyal
NK016(ma)019:136: ba'i byin rlabs bsdus rigs 'dus rgyal ba'i bdag nyid
NK016(ma)019:137: du'o // +aahmh'u a rtsika nertsiga na mo b+ha ga wa te h'u +aahmh'u h'u phata phata snying ba'o //
NK016(ma)019:138: a ya ma du ru tsa sha na sa ma
NK016(ma)019:139: ya badz+ra ga ru ta h'u phata r+aa dza gnod
NK016(ma)019:140: byed kyi snying la m+aa ra ya h'u phata gtso
NK016(ma)019:141: bo'i 'o / badz+ra d+aa ki ni h'u phata de bzhin du /
NK016(ma)019:142: bud+d+ha rat+na pad+ma karma mkha' 'gro lnga'i 'o /
NK016(ma)019:143: badz+ra p+aa ni h'u phata ya m+aan+ta ka h'u phata
NK016(ma)019:144: pad+m+aan+ta krita h'u phata badz+ra yak+sha h'u phata 'khor sngags
NK016(ma)019:145: so // gtso bo'i thugs ka'i phyag rdor gyi thugs srog h'u yig rab tu 'bar //
NK016(ma)019:146: h'u gi 'brug sgra cher sgrog pa'i h'u gi sprin
NK016(ma)019:147: gyis phyogs kun khyab h'u h'u zhes pa h'u sgrub
NK016(ma)019:148: ste rim pa bzhin ci nus bzlas pa'i mthar mchod
NK016(ma)019:149: cing bstod nas / bdun pa 'dod yon gsol ba ni /
NK016(ma)019:150: h'u bde gshegs kun 'dus rdo rje drag po rtsal
NK016(ma)019:151: glog ltar myur ba'i thugs rjes brtser dgongs la sku
NK016(ma)019:152: gsung thugs kyi dbang bskur byin gyis rlobs mchog dang
NK016(ma)019:153: thun mong dngos grub rtsal du gsol ka ya w+aaka
NK016(ma)019:154: tsit+ta sid+d+hi pha la ho zhes dngos grub blang ngo
NK016(ma)019:156: dang po tshogs kyi mchod pa la drug gi dang po ni /
NK016(ma)019:157: h'u thugs las ram yam kham 'phros pas ma dag
NK016(ma)019:158: nyes skyon bsregs gtor sbyangs b+h+r+aum las rin chen snod
NK016(ma)019:159: nang du tshogs rdzas sha lnga bdud rtsi lnga rigs
NK016(ma)019:160: lnga'i dam rdzas 'dod yon rdzas zag med nam mkha'
NK016(ma)019:161: gang bar gyur +aahmh'u hoh zhes byin gyis brlabs /
NK016(ma)019:163: h'u o rgyan gling dang rnga yab gling lang+ka dpal
NK016(ma)019:164: gyi pho brang nas che mchog pad+ma drag po'i tshogs
NK016(ma)019:165: spyan 'dren gnas 'dir gshegs su gsol dza h'u bam
NK016(ma)019:166: hohs spyan drangs / gsum pa tshogs mchod pa ni /
NK016(ma)019:167: gzugs sgra dri ro reg ldan pa'i 'dod yon tshogs
NK016(ma)019:168: kyi mchod pa 'di gus pa'i blo yis 'bul lags
NK016(ma)019:169: na dgyes pa'i gar gyi bzhes su gsol ga na
NK016(ma)019:170: tsakra pu dza kh+aa hi bzhi pa bar bshags ni
NK016(ma)019:171: / thog med dus nas da lta'i bar sgo gsum mi shes bag med pas //
NK016(ma)019:172: nyams chags 'gal 'phrul ci mchis pa de dag thams cad bshags par bgyi zhes dang yig brgya bzla /
NK016(ma)019:174: h'u che mchog pad+ma thod phreng rtsal gtum drag rngam
NK016(ma)019:175: pa'i rang bzhin la yak+sha me dbal skar ltar 'khrug
NK016(ma)019:176: las byed pho nyar bcas pa rnams drag po'i phrin
NK016(ma)019:177: las dus la babs zhing bcu'i dgra dang bgegs rnams
NK016(ma)019:178: kyi gzugs phung rdul phran bzhin du bshig rnam shes
NK016(ma)019:179: chos kyi dbyings su spor n+ri tri sha trum m+aa
NK016(ma)019:180: ra ya rbad zhes bsgral zhing bstab la /
NK016(ma)019:181: dgra bgegs bsgral ba'i sha khrag rus don snying nang
NK016(ma)019:182: rol bcas pa rnams ye shes bdud rtsir byin rlabs
NK016(ma)019:183: nas bzhes shig rol cig dgyes par mdzod mam sa
NK016(ma)019:184: rak+ta ki ni ri ti kh+aa hi tshogs la rol
NK016(ma)019:185: zhing / drug pa lhag ma ni /
NK016(ma)019:186: h'u sngon tshe zhal bzhes dam bcas bzhin dkyil 'khor
NK016(ma)019:187: chen po'i phyi nyul ba'i lhag gtor dbang ba'i srung
NK016(ma)019:188: ma rnams 'dir bzhes bcol pa'i phrin las mdzod uts+tshish+ta
NK016(ma)019:189: ba ling+ta kh+aa hi gnyis pa thugs dam bskul pa
NK016(ma)019:190: ni / h'u bzhengs shig bzhengs shig chos kyi dbyings
NK016(ma)019:191: nas bzhengs dbang brag 'bar ba dpal gyi pho nyar
NK016(ma)019:192: bcas drag po'i phrin las mdzad pa'i dus la babs
NK016(ma)019:193: snyigs dus gdug can dgra bgegs 'byung po'i dpung bod
NK016(ma)019:194: khams phung byed sde dang bcas pa rnams rdzu 'phrul
NK016(ma)019:195: mthu stobs nus pas tshar chod la yang dag lam
NK016(ma)019:196: gyi bde chen rgyas par mdzod gsum pa chad tho
NK016(ma)019:197: ni / ni / h'u sngon tshe bskal pa'i dang
NK016(ma)019:198: po la slob dpon pad+ma thod phreng gis dam la
NK016(ma)019:199: btags pa'i srung ma rnams chos nyid bden pa'i dka'
NK016(ma)019:200: la nyon gdong dmar bod kyi rgyal khams su lha
NK016(ma)019:201: srin sde brgyad dam la btags bdag ni slob dpon
NK016(ma)019:202: de yi brgyud khyod ni lha 'dre g.yar dam can
NK016(ma)019:203: sngon tshe khas blang bka' ma bcag da lta rig
NK016(ma)019:204: 'dzin dam ma 'dral rgyan gyi gtor ma 'di bzhes
NK016(ma)019:205: la bcol pa'i phrin las sgrub par mdzod bzhi pa
NK016(ma)019:206: ni / ni / brtan ma ni / b+h+yo slob
NK016(ma)019:207: dpon pad+ma thod phreng gi bka' nyan ma mo brtan
NK016(ma)019:208: ma'i tshogs dam rdzas dpal gyi gtor ma longs bcol
NK016(ma)019:209: pa'i phrin las sgrub par mdzod lnga pa bro mnan
NK016(ma)019:210: ni / ni / brtan ma ni / ni /
NK016(ma)019:211: h'u nga ni 'jigs byed chen po ste khams gsum
NK016(ma)019:212: thams cad spyi nas gnon dgra bgegs sdig chen 'byung
NK016(ma)019:213: po rnams dus gsum las kyi khung bur mnan mnon
NK016(ma)019:214: no bcing po stam b+ha ya rdo rje bro yis
NK016(ma)019:215: rgyas gdab bo sus kyang 'jig par nus ma yin
NK016(ma)019:216: lam +aa lam h'u lam stam b+ha ya nan drug
NK016(ma)019:217: pa rjes chog la lnga las /
NK016(ma)019:219: sngar bzhin mchod cing bstod la /
NK016(ma)019:220: ma rnyed yongs su ma tshang dang sogs dang yig brgya brjod /
NK016(ma)019:222: 'dir ni rten dang lha na cig tusogs brjod /
NK016(ma)019:223: gsum pa sprul pa bsdu ba ni /
NK016(ma)019:224: h'u chos nyid skye ba med pa las 'gags med
NK016(ma)019:225: rdo rje srin por shar 'gags pa nyid na 'gags
NK016(ma)019:226: med pa // spros bral ka dag klong du thim
NK016(ma)019:227: h'u h'u h'u gis dkyil 'khor thams cad 'od gsal
NK016(ma)019:228: med pa // du bsdu / phata phata phatakyi thun mtshams kyi lha skur ldang ngo //
NK016(ma)019:230: dge 'dis mtha' yas sems can kun khrag 'thung pad+ma
NK016(ma)019:231: drag po yi go 'phang byang chub myur thob nas
NK016(ma)019:232: bdud las rnam par rgyal bar shog lnga pa shis
NK016(ma)019:233: brjod ni / byin rlabs mchog rtsol rigs brgya'i bdag
NK016(ma)019:234: bla ma rnams kyi bkra shis shog dngos grub char
NK016(ma)019:235: 'bebs zhi dang khro'i yi dam lha tshogs thogs med
NK016(ma)019:236: phrin las sgrub mdzad pa'i dpa' bo mkha' 'gro'i gang
NK016(ma)019:237: la bsam pa'i don kun 'grub dge legs mchog gi
NK016(ma)019:238: bkra shis shog zhes brjod do drag dmar bka' ma
NK016(ma)019:239: 'o bran lugs kyi gzhung snga 'gyur bstan pa'i nyi
NK016(ma)019:240: ma o rgyan gter bdag gling pa'i sgrubs thabs 'dod
NK016(ma)019:241: 'jo'i bum bzang las 'byung ba gzhir bzhag gter chen
NK016(ma)019:242: nyid kyi zab gter drag dmar gyi rdo rje'i tshig
NK016(ma)019:243: gis zhal bskang ste bklag pas grub par sh+ai la
NK016(ma)019:244: b+ha dra'i zhal 'don du pad+ma ma nis bris pa
